{
  "design_notes": "S0 introduces the core rhythm with a strong bass hold and clear transitions. S1 ramps up the lane switching leading into the drop. S2 has been completely redesigned to avoid repetitive L-C-R patterns, utilizing dynamic pairs of jacks, balanced lane switches, and syncopated holds. S3 replaces the previous monotone sweep with highly structured 4-bar alternating patterns: doublets, zig-zags, mirrors, and anchored sweeps. S4 extends the final sequence using grid-placements through the entire outro, bringing the chart to a satisfying and complete conclusion.",
  "sections": [
